OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,FThe leader of the Welsh Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats, Jane Dodds, said Welsh
OL,8,FLabour "deserve to lose" at the Senedd
OL,9,FElection in May.
OL,11,FSpeaking at her party's campaign
OL,12,Flaunch in Swansea on Wednesday, 8
OL,13,FApril she said whilst Labour does not
OL,14,Fdeserve to hold onto power, "Reform
OL,15,Fand Plaid Cymru don't deserve to win"
OL,16,Feither.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
