OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775675473
OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,FShe said her party "will play a key
OL,7,Frole" when it comes to forming a new
OL,8,FWelsh Government, with the strategy of
OL,9,Fworking on "hyper-local campaigns" in
OL,10,Fthe hopes to win an additional "three
OL,11,For four" seats in the Senedd.
OL,13,F"I've been there (the Senedd) on my
OL,14,Fown, like 'Billy no-mates'. I want a
OL,15,Fteam behind me and we are going to be
OL,16,Fdelivering on key positive messages,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
