OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,FThe party highlighted key areas
OL,7,Fdescribed as "red lines" they will not
OL,8,Fnegotiate on when it comes to working
OL,9,Fwith other political parties.
OL,11,FThese include protecting the NHS by
OL,12,Fbetter funding social care, not
OL,13,Fspending any money on Welsh
OL,14,Findependence planning, free childcare
OL,15,F(ages nine months to four years) for
OL,16,F30 hours a week, reforming business
OL,17,Frates to help high streets, and
OL,18,Fcleaning up Welsh rivers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
