OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775675473
OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,FDodds emphasised that her party will
OL,7,F"not spend a penny" on Welsh
OL,8,Findependence, compared to the Green
OL,9,FParty and Plaid Cymru.
OL,11,FShe said: "We do know that the leader
OL,12,Fof Plaid has talked about doing a
OL,13,Fpiece for work with the Welsh public
OL,14,Faround consultation discussions, a
OL,15,Fplan to talk with them about
OL,16,Findependence, and what it could
OL,17,Fdeliver for Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
