PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1775675473
OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,F"We are really clear, not a penny of
OL,7,FWelsh Government money should be spent
OL,8,Fon independence, it should all go into
OL,9,Fpublic services."
OL,11,FIn the last Senedd Election in 2021,
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Liberal Democrats only
OL,13,Fmanaged to secure one seat.
OL,15,FLatest polling by ITV Cymru Wales
OL,16,Fshows the party could only win 5% of
OL,17,Fthe overall vote share, which would
OL,18,Fleave Dodds party with no
OL,19,Frepresentation from May.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
