OL,3,CWelsh Labour 'deserve to lose' says
OL,4,CLib Dem Leader at campaign launch
OL,6,FDodds challenged the latest polling
OL,7,Ffigures saying they are "very small
OL,8,Fsamples" that do not have the
OL,9,F"experience of a PR (proportional
OL,10,Frepresentation) election".
OL,12,FWhen asked if her party would
OL,13,Ftherefore collaborate with the likes
OL,14,Fof Reform UK, Dodds said "absolutely
OL,15,Fnot".
OL,17,FShe said: "We have ruled out the
OL,18,FConservatives and Reform and let's see
OL,19,Fwhat happens in the next four or five
OL,20,Fweeks and let's see what those parties
OL,21,Fcome to us with.
